我来帮你优化这个流程图，让它更美观、专业：

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>优化流程图</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .flow-column {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .flow-column:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .column-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea;
        }

        .flow-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .flow-box:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
        }

        .formula-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            color: #2c3e50;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .note-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #856404;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .arrow {
            text-align: center;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 30px;
            margin: -10px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .loop-arrow {
            text-align: center;
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .column-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .flow-box {
                font-size: 16px;
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Muon 列 -->
        <div class="flow-column">
            <div class="column-title">🔷 Muon</div>

            <div class="flow-box">M</div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">NS 迭代</div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">Update</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Shampoo/Soap 列 -->
        <div class="flow-column">
            <div class="column-title">🔶 Shampoo/Soap</div>

            <div class="flow-box">M</div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="formula-box">
                L = GG<sup>T</sup> , &nbsp;&nbsp; R = G<sup>T</sup>G
            </div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">
                L<sup>-¼</sup> M R<sup>-¼</sup>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box" style="padding: 25px;">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    ‖M<sub>adam</sub>‖ / ‖L<sup>-¼</sup>MR<sup>-¼</sup>‖
                </div>
                <div style="font-size: 20px; margin: 5px 0;">·</div>
                <div>
                    (L<sup>-¼</sup> M R<sup>-¼</sup>)
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="note-box">
                <strong>📌 SOAP:</strong><br>
                额外维护一套<br>
                Adam 的步长
            </div>

            <div class="loop-arrow">↻ 循环更新</div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">Update</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mousse 列 -->
        <div class="flow-column">
            <div class="column-title">🔷 Mousse</div>

            <div class="flow-box">M</div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="formula-box">
                L = GG<sup>T</sup> , &nbsp;&nbsp; R = G<sup>T</sup>G
            </div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">
                L<sup>-¼</sup> M R<sup>-¼</sup>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">NS 迭代</div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">
                L<sup>-¼</sup> M R<sup>-¼</sup>
            </div>
            <div class="arrow">↓</div>

            <div class="flow-box">Update</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

**主要优化点：**

1. ✨ **现代渐变背景** - 使用紫色渐变替代单调背景
2. 🎨 **卡片式设计** - 每列独立卡片，增加阴影和圆角
3. 📱 **响应式布局** - 自适应不同屏幕尺寸
4. 🎯 **交互效果** - 鼠标悬停时卡片和按钮有动画
5. 🔤 **更好的字体** - 使用现代无衬线字体
6. 📊 **清晰的层次** - 用颜色和图标区分不同部分
7. 💡 **视觉引导** - 箭头和颜色引导视觉流向

将代码保存为 `.html` 文件即可在浏览器中查看效果！
